# Project Rules & Guidelines

This project follows strict coding standards and best practices. All AI agents and developers must adhere to these rules.

## üìö AI Rules Documentation

This project includes comprehensive AI agent rules located in the `.ai-rules/` folder. These rules MUST be followed for all code changes:

### Core Documentation Files

1. **`.ai-rules/README.md`** - Overview and quick reference
2. **`.ai-rules/CODING_STANDARDS.md`** - TypeScript and component standards
3. **`.ai-rules/COMPONENT_GUIDELINES.md`** - Component development best practices
